{"tid":1457610,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"俾人分化緊 大家小心","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:28:42.000Z","uid":154875,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"240eb41e7a0d3e515ac9ed5256690d3c5ac56eaa","tid":1457610,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">資訊不完全根本冇人有責任</span><br />\n班狗今日嘅行為根本我地就冇消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有人都估估下<br />\n我唔排除都有人放假消息<br />\n但係我地可以睇到機場個邊啲人都開始走<br />\n有證據睇到有可能強行清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過昨日嘅事睇得出根本啲狗開始唔理形象<br />\n係機場放tg都好有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係機場依個環境<br />\n假如職員同遊客走曬<br />\n啲狗只要封死個出口<br />\n[/size=6]啲手足根本冇機會走[/size=6]<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如佢地今日真係強沖<br />\n手足俾人拉曬又會俾人話做咩唔走，be water<br />\n<br />\n依家出面好多po係度互屌緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正正中左班撚樣嘅局</span><br />\n[/size=6][/red]攻城為下 攻心為上[/red][/size=6]<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得走係保存到大家<br />\n一俾佢地捉就咩都冇<br />\n<br />\n理性撒退並唔係輸<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">只係下次更有力嘅反擊</span></span></strong><br />\n記住我地係不分化不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地就係分化緊我地<br />\n唔好咁傻豬豬中左佢地班狗嘅計<br />\n<br />\nBtw第一次開po，有咩錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07066a7f9747788be12b40b19dbe16f4b9f02f88","tid":1457610,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8282a88641c61f32a2a72e5f9ceb4def04f912","tid":1457610,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:57:3